# Sellers.json Daily Update Crontab
#
# To install:
# 1. Edit this file with your actual project path
# 2. Run: crontab -e
# 3. Add the line below (adjust time as needed)
#
# Format: minute hour day month weekday command
# This runs daily at 2:00 AM

# Daily update at 2:00 AM
0 2 * * * /Users/butterfly/.claude/newdev/seller-json/scripts/run-daily-update.sh

# Alternative: Run every 6 hours
# 0 */6 * * * /Users/butterfly/.claude/newdev/seller-json/scripts/run-daily-update.sh

# Alternative: Run at midnight
# 0 0 * * * /Users/butterfly/.claude/newdev/seller-json/scripts/run-daily-update.sh

# Check logs at: /Users/butterfly/.claude/newdev/seller-json/logs/
